==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Interposer
<hw>In`ter*pos"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who, or that
which, interposes or intervenes; an obstacle or interruption; a mediator
or agent between parties.</def> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Interposit</ent>⟦br⟧
